ActCanada Post Corporation Act
PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE NON-MAILABLE MATTER REGULATIONS which must come into effect by July14, 2008 stipulate that sexually explicit material is unacceptable for mailing as addressed admail or unaddressed admail unless it is contained in an opaque envelope bearing a warning that it contains adult material.
